Uses of Package
org.jscsi.initiator

Packages that use org.jscsi.initiator
org.jscsi.initiator This package contains all the core classes to provide an easy and usable iSCSI (RFC 3720) initiator. 
org.jscsi.initiator.connection This package contains all the states of a connection and all phases of the iSCSI (RFC 3720) implementation. 
 

Classes in org.jscsi.initiator used by org.jscsi.initiator
Configuration
          Configuration This class stores all informations, which are set during an iSCSI Session, Connection or are set as the default values.
Initiator
          Initiator This class represents an initiator, which request messages to a target defined by the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).
 

Classes in org.jscsi.initiator used by org.jscsi.initiator.connection
Configuration
          Configuration This class stores all informations, which are set during an iSCSI Session, Connection or are set as the default values.
LinkFactory
          LinkFactory Implements a Factory which enables the Initiator to switch between multithreaded and singlethreaded modes.
